content:
5 DEAD: A TODDLER, 10 YEAR OLD, AND 3 YOUNG PEOPLE KILLED IN NYC HOUSE FIRE:  
WHAT'S THE CAUSE ?? The story is horrific.  The single-family house in Queens erupted in flames Sunday afternoon about 2:38pm. The youngest victim was a 2 year old boy.  Another 10 year old boy perished, along with 3 females: 16, 17 and 20.  The children's grandfather, 46, managed to roll out of a 2nd story window.  Fire marshals AND the NYPD are at the scene.  It's the largest, single loss of life in a NYC fire since 2015, when a Brooklyn mom lost 7 of her 8 children in a house fire. Here's a report from Anthony DiLorenzo of PIX 11
name: Mary Murphy Mystery

content: MYSTERY: WHAT HAPPENED TO AZIZ CHIRKEEV?  He's only 20 years old, and his mom saved her money to bring him to Brooklyn from Kyrgyzstan last July.  He was living in Brighton Beach and working at a dentist's office in Sheepshead Bay for just two weeks.  Aziz vanished, after finishing his shift at Mizrahi Orthodontics on Monday night, April 3rd.  He called his mom and said he was going to McDonald's--and then taking a train to Manhattan to see Central Park. He hasn't been heard from since.  His mother is full of anguish.  Please watch the attached clip and contact police if you know anything.  Thank you.
name: Mary Murphy Mystery

content: TEARS FOR THE CHILDREN:  PIX 11 prepared this photo collage as a tribute for the five, young people who died in a raging fire in #QueensVillage this past Sunday.  The youngest was 2 year old Jayce Lipford, seen on the upper left.  His cousin, Melody Edwards--17--is below him in the collage, with flowers in her hair. She was visiting her friend, Jada Foxworth, 16--wearing the beige sweater--before the fire broke out.  Jada's older sister, Destiny Dones, 20--in the pink shirt--is seen above Jada.  In the middle of the collage, we see 10 year old Rashawn Matthews.  The FDNY and NYPD are both investigating the cause of the fire. Many of the victims were trapped in the attack. 2 men, including a grandfather, got out.

Zire King is wanted for the 'point-blank' execution of his girlfriend, 41 year old Jacqueline Dicks--a mother of six. content: CVS STORE GUY CONNED TEENS INTO SEX PHOTOS:  The NYPD says 29 year old Jose Ramos wasn't very clever, after all.  Detectives from the Brooklyn Special Victims Squad say as far back as November, he was accusing teen girls of shoplifting--and then bringing them to a room, where he allegedly took photos of their vaginas and breasts.  He's accused of making them sign phony "consent forms"--telling them if they told police, they'd be arrested.  On Monday, he was accused in one case--and by Wednesday, he was arrested again, charged in three more abuse cases.  Police say Ramos was dumb enough to keep the phony consent forms, and when they busted him, they found the names of ALL his alleged victims.
name: Mary Murphy Mystery

content:
MISSING #KRYGYZ SON BELIEVED TO HAVE JUMPED FROM BROOKLYN BRIDGE: 
It's a heart-breaking development for the mother of 20 year old, Aziz CHIRKEEV. Her son had joined her in New York from the Kyrgyz Republic last July. He went missing on April 3rd, after finishing his shift at a dental office in Sheepshead Bay.  His body was found near a Sunset Park pier Sunday. The Medical Examiner made a positive identification Wednesday.  CHIRKEEV had told his mother he wanted to take the train to Central Park. He apparently did that--and then went to the Brooklyn Bridge. We will have a complete recap of Aziz' story shortly on pix11.com.
name: Mary Murphy Mystery
title: Timeline Photos

content: EL CHAPO WIFE INSPIRES 'KIM KARDASHIAN-LIKE' FRENZY:  The 27 year old, beauty queen wife of jailed, Mexican drug billionaire El Chapo De Sinaloa caused a bit of media chaos outside federal court in Brooklyn Friday.  Emma Coronel--the mother of El Chapo's twin girls--emerged wearing a glamorous, white pants suit in the pouring rain.  A judge ruled the 60-year old Joaquin Archivaldo Guzman Loera--known as El Chapo (Shorty)--can only communicate with his wife by pre-screened mail.  He's accused of pumping tons of cocaine, heroin and marijuana into the United States through his murderous Sinaloa cartel. Full report at 5 pm on PIX 11 News.
name: Mary Murphy Mystery

content: YOUR U.S. TAX DOLLARS PAYING FOR EL CHAPO'S DEFENSE: We wanted him, and now we're paying for El Chapo De Sinaloa!  Lawyers for the Mexican drug billionaire said he's been suffering from "auditory hallucinations" in solitary, but he very lucidly told a Brooklyn federal judge Friday he wants to keep the U.S. public defenders that have been assigned to represent him.  This is the guy accused of sending "hit squads" to kill police officers and politicians south of the border--and pumping tons of heroin into our country.  His young, GLAMOROUS wife #EmmaCoronel waved and smiled to him at the hearing.  Check out the chaos of the morning, in the POURING RAIN, that we captured with our camera.
name: Mary Murphy Mystery

PIX 11 has a picture of suspect, Keon Robinson, a registered sex offender who's now a suspect in 3 robberies in the 32nd Precinct.

the NYPD has pulled a man's body out of a lake in Central Park.  The latest was Wednesday morning, when a man's body was discovered in Swan Lake by 59th Street and Fifth Avenue.  On Tuesday, a man's body was found floating in the #CentralPark reservoir near West 90th Street and Central Park West.  NYPD Chief of Detectives Robert Boyce was going to speak about the 2 incidents on Wednesday.
name: Mary Murphy Mystery

robbery and sexual assault of a tourist from Germany.  They found him in Schenectady County, in upstate New York.  The NYPD said Robinson robbed three people during a brutal crime spree, ending with the 31-year old tourist on May 4th.  She had left the subway near West 149th Street at 2:50 am and was heading back to her Airbnb in Harlem, when she was assaulted.  The attack was so brutal that she had some of her teeth knocked out.

One aviation expert told PIX 11 there were reports the plane flipped over before it crashed, perhaps affected by a "microburst" weather event.  The plane had taken off for Philadelphia bound for Teterboro.

content: "I HAVE A SICKNESS"  A mob scene at federal court, after former U.S. Congressman and mayoral candidate, #AnthonyWeiner, pleaded guilty to 'sexting' with a girl he knew was 15.  Weiner sobbed as he read his statement to Judge Loretta Preska, telling her, "Beginning with my service in Congress and continuing into the first half of last year, I have compulsively sought attention from women who contacted me on social media."  Prosecutors have recommended Weiner be sentenced to between 21 and 27 months in prison.  A judge could give him no jail time...or up to 10 years.  Weiner's estranged wife--Hillary Clinton's chief aide, Huma Abedin--filed for divorce within hours of the guilty plea.  The couple has a young son.  Weiner said he is getting daily treatment for his "sickness." Thank you to PIX 11's Dan Mannarino for the footage.
name: Mary Murphy Mystery

TIMES SQUARE DRIVER FACING MURDER CHARGE--AND 20 COUNTS OF ATTEMPTED MURDER:
26 year old RIchard Rojas of the Bronx was in court Friday, accused of Murder in the 2nd degree and 20 counts of attempted murder, for mowing down pedestrians in Times Square, New York City Thursday at noontime.  18 year old Alyssa Ehlson of Michigan, in NYC with her mother and sister, died at the scene. Police said Rojas, a US Navy vet, was screaming and rambling about hearing voices, when he was grabbed on 7th Avenue.  He also told police he had "smoked something"--and toxicology tests will determine if that "something" was K2, a  synthetic drug that's made with chemicals sprayed on dried leaves..
